Cell["\<\
When none of the definitions are general enough, Wolfram Language will store \
and try definitions in the order provided by the user.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"8c89a166-96e9-43a1-92b6-9d6491c1fa0d"],

Cell["\<\
Here is another function that works differently for an even or odd input:\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"305851e7-8d08-4449-a9e2-7c4e063062cd"],

