Cell["\<\
UpValues can be used to build a database of properties for an object. You can \
associate each definition you make with the object that it concerns, rather \
than with the property you are specifying:\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"c8dbaf8f-9ce7-47f0-ae2f-023b9b125c70"],

